{
  "texts": [
    "Physician specialities included endocrinology, dermatology, cardiology, epidemiology, otorhinolaryngology, infectious disease, ophthalmology and hematology-oncology.",
    "Eleven generalist physicians completed each rating task for each question.",
    "Three-way utility ranking.",
    "Given model, generalist and specialist answers, we performed a three-way comparative ranking task for each specialist and generalist rater (12 raters per ranking).",
    "Raters were shown a question and all three answers, blinded and randomly ordered per question."
  ]
}